| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2336 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b48613fc-0b7a-5d8b-b280-c4ff1eef19a5"
